WEBVTT

00:10:28.701 --> 00:10:33.870
in which African Americans
had been on that soil at that time.

00:10:34.707 --> 00:10:39.124
It had not happened
in 12 generations of enslavement

00:10:39.148 --> 00:10:42.198
that preceded
nearly a century of Jim Crow.

00:10:43.489 --> 00:10:45.949
How many "greats"

00:10:45.973 --> 00:10:49.203
do you have to add
to the word "grandparent"

00:10:49.227 --> 00:10:55.324
to begin to imagine how long
enslavement lasted in the United States?

00:10:56.715 --> 00:11:02.977
Secondly, this Great Migration
